2e741458-73e8-4cf6-98d1-db121d557448.title: Note
2e741458-73e8-4cf6-98d1-db121d557448.text: Edmond moves down into the sewers at this step.

8fa2d271-cf5f-4047-9cf6-1703922ebf50.title: Note
8fa2d271-cf5f-4047-9cf6-1703922ebf50.text: Edmond moves back to the garden at this step.

9cc030f8-3c9d-48ed-afaa-36f8d17e2420.title: Edmond
9cc030f8-3c9d-48ed-afaa-36f8d17e2420.text: Sorry, I can't stop to talk...

799d66ee-ee1f-4572-85ab-c1915607377c.title: Edmond
799d66ee-ee1f-4572-85ab-c1915607377c.text:
I've got to find my daughter. I pray that she is still
alive...

2c969547-3be0-4ddb-959d-b46e609f737e.title: Edmond
2c969547-3be0-4ddb-959d-b46e609f737e.text:
Elena's a healer. Three weeks ago she managed to
cross the wall into West Ardougne. No one's allowed to
cross the wall in case they spread the plague.

af41ca40-dcd6-4a3a-9fe9-97863afb96ce.title: Edmond
af41ca40-dcd6-4a3a-9fe9-97863afb96ce.text:
Not that long ago, West Ardougne was hit by a deadly
plague. They had the wall built to try and keep it
contained. No one is allowed to enter the city now
apart from the mourners.

86a17d6b-e476-457b-a0f2-4e33092be0bb.title: Edmond
86a17d6b-e476-457b-a0f2-4e33092be0bb.text:
They say the plague is a horrible way to go... That's
why Elena felt she had to go help. She said she'd be
gone for a few days but we've heard nothing since.

bd585930-d253-4965-8c69-e13366c778d2.title: <player>
bd585930-d253-4965-8c69-e13366c778d2.text: Maybe I could help find her?

6062cc4e-d5a3-4c55-a393-2eee8f0d6394.title: Edmond
6062cc4e-d5a3-4c55-a393-2eee8f0d6394.text:
Really, would you? I've been working on a plan to get
into West Ardougne, but I'm too old and tired to carry
it through. But you on the other hand, you should have
no problem.

8381319c-9f31-405a-8a95-58f24a9627b1.title: Would you like to start Plague City?

6457532b-c68d-462c-8468-d51624708cd7.title: <player>
6457532b-c68d-462c-8468-d51624708cd7.text: On second thoughts, I'd better not.

0ebaf95e-e40d-45ac-be4f-ef5885a76962.title: Edmond
0ebaf95e-e40d-45ac-be4f-ef5885a76962.text: Well if you hear anything about Elena please tell me.

0c8b2dd5-fdcd-4aca-bdf3-303e414642ab.title: Edmond
0c8b2dd5-fdcd-4aca-bdf3-303e414642ab.text:
If you're going into West Ardougne you'll need
protection from the plague. My wife made a special gas
mask for Elena with dwellberries rubbed into it.

4e5eb415-9aeb-46c8-be19-a23bec2c4180.title: Edmond
4e5eb415-9aeb-46c8-be19-a23bec2c4180.text:
They help to repel the plague apparently. We need
some more though...

af0ecaec-ef0f-4a3f-b980-2d7898a6cf37.title: <player>
af0ecaec-ef0f-4a3f-b980-2d7898a6cf37.text: Where can I find these dwellberries?

7074ba3a-086b-40c9-ab0e-b9f75a5fa838.title: Edmond
7074ba3a-086b-40c9-ab0e-b9f75a5fa838.text:
The only place I know of is McGrubor's Wood, just
west of Seers' Village. The berries are bright blue so
they're easy to spot.

4f8eb2bd-d708-4e91-8930-64ab84d37205.title: <player>
4f8eb2bd-d708-4e91-8930-64ab84d37205.text: Okay, I'll go and get some.

210b9e93-d016-4b73-a2df-e7a699ff0c72.title: Edmond
210b9e93-d016-4b73-a2df-e7a699ff0c72.text:
The foresters keep a close eye on it, but there is a back
way in.

3910c62c-e3a7-474c-9653-a2548d452794.title: Edmond
3910c62c-e3a7-474c-9653-a2548d452794.text: Have you got the dwellberries yet?

919230ec-b516-4776-9b96-a6a273a09abb.title: Edmond
919230ec-b516-4776-9b96-a6a273a09abb.text:
You'll probably find them in McGrubor's Wood, just
west of Seers' Village. The berries are bright blue so
they're easy to spot.

65af79cf-f998-4037-b8a5-c6fc34ee9b05.title: <player>
65af79cf-f998-4037-b8a5-c6fc34ee9b05.text: Okay, I'll go and get some.

36265ed6-0ae1-41fe-aed0-5741d988265b.title: Edmond
36265ed6-0ae1-41fe-aed0-5741d988265b.text:
The foresters keep a close eye on it, but there is a back
way in.

d48ac950-3ecc-4bcf-af82-39b971c16677.title: Edmond
d48ac950-3ecc-4bcf-af82-39b971c16677.text: Take them to my wife Alrena, she's inside.

4cc690bf-3628-4e51-8496-184429e519a3.title: <player>
4cc690bf-3628-4e51-8496-184429e519a3.text: Hi Edmond, I've got the gas mask now.

8c54d18f-c400-401a-a151-538e377f8082.title: Edmond
8c54d18f-c400-401a-a151-538e377f8082.text:
Good stuff, now for the digging. Beneath us are the
Ardougne sewers. I've done some research, and I
reckon you can use them to access to West Ardougne.

ac2f8971-cec6-469c-a235-953cd0d16573.title: Edmond
ac2f8971-cec6-469c-a235-953cd0d16573.text:
I've already tried digging down to them but the soil is
rock hard. You'll need to pour on several buckets of
water to soften it up. I reckon four buckets should do
it.

be5263aa-d1b5-4024-be13-348ccb5a8300.title: Note
be5263aa-d1b5-4024-be13-348ccb5a8300.text: set to pour buckets of water

ab66cd53-b57e-4bc1-be1e-362494d67afb.title: <player>
ab66cd53-b57e-4bc1-be1e-362494d67afb.text:
I still need to pour four more buckets of water on the
soil.

2dab629d-9328-4931-81ad-57cbbb50e5f5.title: <player>
2dab629d-9328-4931-81ad-57cbbb50e5f5.text:
I still need to pour three more buckets of water on the
soil.

327da12e-e407-414d-b54d-498ee373fdbc.title: <player>
327da12e-e407-414d-b54d-498ee373fdbc.text:
I still need to pour two more buckets of water on the
soil.

86b979e6-0a4e-4c0d-a444-c2f7598b5a63.title: <player>
86b979e6-0a4e-4c0d-a444-c2f7598b5a63.text:
I still need to pour one more bucket of water on the
soil.

a3cb4c21-6fd2-43c9-9fac-3e5902b7f086.title: <player>
a3cb4c21-6fd2-43c9-9fac-3e5902b7f086.text: I've soaked the soil with water.

399b613c-8007-4735-8f4f-9ffc1da39a5d.title: Edmond
399b613c-8007-4735-8f4f-9ffc1da39a5d.text:
That's great, it should be soft enough to dig through
now. There should be a spade nearby that you can use.

9b544b95-58ac-46fb-9cf2-1bb5bb673ebe.title: Edmond
9b544b95-58ac-46fb-9cf2-1bb5bb673ebe.text:
I think it's the pipe to the south that comes up in West
Ardougne.

65f7966d-fa14-4f6c-a9c9-a87017dfceea.title: <player>
65f7966d-fa14-4f6c-a9c9-a87017dfceea.text:
Edmond, I can't get through to West Ardougne!
There's an iron grill blocking my way, I can't pull it off
alone.

86a946a4-fc4f-46bd-8e2e-d739296bcdb0.title: Edmond
86a946a4-fc4f-46bd-8e2e-d739296bcdb0.text:
If you get some rope you could tie to the grill, then we
could both pull it at the same time.

ce83f9d4-0eaa-44e6-b48d-24d253407838.title: <player>
ce83f9d4-0eaa-44e6-b48d-24d253407838.text:
I've tied a rope to the grill over there, will you help me
pull it off?

2b8991bb-90af-474a-aba8-9d9a6fe75237.title: Edmond
2b8991bb-90af-474a-aba8-9d9a6fe75237.text:
Once you're in the city look for a man called Jethick.
He's an old friend of the family. Hopefully he can help
you.

57ac53ba-c13a-4493-bc98-01ba9238ab99.title: Note
57ac53ba-c13a-4493-bc98-01ba9238ab99.text:
set to find Jethick
remove grill from
the pipe and allow access

77129e94-11b9-4014-8dcd-171ba8887884.title: <player>
77129e94-11b9-4014-8dcd-171ba8887884.text: Not yet, it's a big city over there.

4d01a57d-afe5-45a3-b564-335d0417a401.title: Edmond
4d01a57d-afe5-45a3-b564-335d0417a401.text: I hope it's not too late.

a1019576-c294-49cc-916b-9cf7da67f56b.title: <player>
a1019576-c294-49cc-916b-9cf7da67f56b.text:
Not yet, it's a big city over there. Do you have a
picture of Elena?

234695d3-5e8f-4312-a880-50dc138e829e.title: Edmond
234695d3-5e8f-4312-a880-50dc138e829e.text:
There should be a picture of Elena in the house. Please
find her quickly, I hope it's not too late.

a56fac00-47fe-4397-ba6f-1a5f2ed5bbfb.title: <player>
a56fac00-47fe-4397-ba6f-1a5f2ed5bbfb.text: Not yet, it's a big city over there.

b5f187bc-1721-4d7e-9f0a-2f9eb8d9a21e.title: Edmond
b5f187bc-1721-4d7e-9f0a-2f9eb8d9a21e.text: I hope it's not too late.

511195f7-cde3-4737-97f6-f7613f15a0b3.title: Edmond
511195f7-cde3-4737-97f6-f7613f15a0b3.text:
Thank you, thank you! Elena beat you back by
minutes. Now I said I'd give you a reward. What can
I give you as a reward I wonder? Here take this magic
scroll, I have little use for it but it may help you.

38dce20a-9094-4465-b8a0-4b461666f0e7.title: Congratulations!
38dce20a-9094-4465-b8a0-4b461666f0e7.text:
You have completed Plague City!

You are awarded:
1 Quest Point
2,425 Mining XP
An Ardougne Teleport Scroll

dd5ae7e3-cbd6-4e67-9087-a447c0e7a406.title: Note
dd5ae7e3-cbd6-4e67-9087-a447c0e7a406.text:
Ardougne teleport scroll
'Maybe I should read it...'

1787b414-9117-4927-9d22-b2ee3a215086.title: Edmond
1787b414-9117-4927-9d22-b2ee3a215086.text:
Now I'd recommend you go and see Elena. She'll want
to thank you herself. She lives in the house opposite
ours.

a52b3917-8c85-4bb8-a4f8-b32a24b7ba9e.title: Note
a52b3917-8c85-4bb8-a4f8-b32a24b7ba9e.text:
Reading the scroll unlocks
the ability to teleport to
East Ardy

94b882ad-3e75-42d8-9242-a0b6055a0eb4.title: Note
94b882ad-3e75-42d8-9242-a0b6055a0eb4.text:
if these items are in your inventory
they will disappear:
(plague_city) key
elena portrait
a scruffy note
warrant

The plague house becomes free to visit whenever,
and the cell is free to enter/exit whenever

d8172bb2-4812-4822-92d7-eb80e54ad958.title: Edmond
d8172bb2-4812-4822-92d7-eb80e54ad958.text: Ah hello. Thank you again for rescuing my daughter.
